#id=1
#text=I need to bake a cake for my friend 's birthday .
#id=2
#text=I have decided to buy a store cake mix to save some time .
#id=3
#text=I decide to get a Devil 's Food cake mix , since that is her favorite .
#id=4
#text=I drive to the store , and head to the isle that has cake mixes .
#id=5
#text=I find the cake mix I want and purchase it .
#id=6
#text=I also check the back of the box to be sure I have all the ingredients I will need , like eggs , oil , etc. .
#id=7
#text=I bring the cake mix home and get started .
#id=8
#text=I read the instructions which tell me to preheat the oven .
#id=9
#text=I get all my ingredients in front of me and read the instructions to mix them properly .
#text=I get my cake pan out and prep it , as that is what the instructions say to do .
#text=I mix my cake ingredients in a bowl and pour this mixture into the pan and place it in the oven for the time listed on the instructions .
#text=When the cake is done baking , I take it out of the oven and let it cool off .
